description:
God cursed the ground for man's sake and then again because of Cain. There is a double curse upon the ground, in addition to that people are not taking care of the ground. Soil depletion continues to increase because of conventional farming practices, overgrazing, deforestation and improper land use. Let us ask God for a piece of land that we can by his grace take care of and grow food organically which adds life to the soil that God may bless the ground we live in.

Contact: gardenevangelist@gmail.com 
Happy Planting!  

Please watch this video to learn how to plant trees using God's Given Method:
"Seed Time and Harvest: God's Way to Plant a Fruit Tree" https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aVVsE3vCV4g
